The story of a new world, one in which fairy tales and modern-day life collide. Emma Swan (Jennifer Morrison) is comfortable in her life as a bail bonds collector when Henry -- the child she gave up a decade earlier -- suddenly shows up. After returning Henry home, Emma decides to stay in town to keep an eye on him and discovers he may not be wrong after all.
